{"remainingRequest":"E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\node_modules\\vue-loader\\lib\\index.js??ref--1-1!E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\node_modules\\@vuepress\\markdown-loader\\index.js??ref--1-2!E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\src\\_posts\\2019-10-21-JavaScript中的“直接操作文档”.md?vue&type=script&lang=js&","dependencies":[{"path":"E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\src\\_posts\\2019-10-21-JavaScript中的“直接操作文档”.md","mtime":1647190307758},{"path":"E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\node_modules\\cache-loader\\dist\\cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\node_modules\\vue-loader\\lib\\index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"E:\\MyCode\\VuePress\\vuepress-blog\\node_modules\\@vuepress\\markdown-loader\\index.js","mtime":499162500000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":[{"type":"Buffer","data":"base64:"},{"version":3,"sources":["2019-10-21-JavaScript中的“直接操作文档”.md"],"names":[],"mappings":";;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;AAwDA","file":"2019-10-21-JavaScript中的“直接操作文档”.md","sourceRoot":"src/_posts","sourcesContent":["<template>\n<ContentSlotsDistributor :slot-key=\"$parent.slotKey\"><p><strong>直接操作文档</strong></p>\n<p>这是最佳的方式，尽量使用这种方式来<em>与网页和用户交互</em>。**使用JavaScript可以访获取用户输入的值，修改HTML或样式，更新网页的内容，全面控制页面。**这些都是利用浏览器的文档对象模型（后面将更详细地讨论）实现的。这是与用户交流的最佳方式。然而，要使用文档对象模型，你必须知道网页的结构，并熟悉用来读写网页的编程接口。</p>\n<p>使用<strong>innerHTML</strong>写入到HTML元素。</p>\n<p>学过HTML/CSS样式，都知道，网页由标签将信息组织起来，而<em>标签的id属性值是唯一的</em>，就像是每人有一个身份证号一样，只要通过身份证号就可以找到相对应的人。那么在网页中，我们通过id先找到标签，然后进行操作。</p>\n<p>语法:</p>\n<p>document.getElementById(“id”)</p>\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<blockquote>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title> Sample Page!</title>\n</head> \n<body> \n<p id=\"demo\">我的第一个段落</p>\n</body>\n</html>\n</blockquote>\n<p>以上JavaScript语句可以在web浏览器中行：\ndocument.getElementById(&quot;demo&quot;) 是使用id属性来查找HTML元素的JavaScript代码。\ninnerHTML = &quot;段落已修改。&quot; 是用于修改元素的HTML内容(innerHTML)的JavaScript代码。</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language- extra-class\"><!--afterbegin--><pre><code>具体应用：\n实现点击左边的图片，右边的文字被更换\n</code></pre>\n<!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-handlebars extra-class\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>box<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">TuPian</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>demo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>javascript<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">TuPian</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\tstr<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'hellow world!'</span>\n\t\t\t\tdocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"demo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><p>css样式：</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-handlebars extra-class\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code>\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token selector\">img</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token selector\">div #demo</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><p>以上大部分内容来自“中国大学mooc”，本文章经本人总结而来，仅是学习参考。</p>\n</ContentSlotsDistributor>\n</template>\n<script>\ndocument.getElementById(\"demo\").innerHTML = \"段落已修改。\";\n\n\n</script>\n\n\n"]}]}